{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"symbolKind":"class","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B39ThemeControlItemComponentTokensProviderC","roleHeading":"Class","title":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for components with a ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"control item"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" layout like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSSwitch","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSRadioButton","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSCheckboItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/Orang